{"id": "1181192502104035458", "channel_id": "1181192502104035458", "type": 0, "author_id": "1179326256920137780", "author_name": "wutaa1", "author_bot": false, "content": "打無光送的艾瑞卡大家有拿到嘛？艾瑞卡搭配三小強很好用！！想要感受體驗下超維玩法但還沒開始抽超維的可以根據這個攻略體驗下（這個搭配三小強，難度上會比其他超維搭配低一些～） ​​​\n今後整理的相關攻略文都會存放在谷歌表單：https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1ahF_ULcWsj8Up9hT6qNzraKoE3Vlyhni/edit?usp=sharing&ouid=109622897795166533791&rtpof=true&sd=true\n有需要的守密人可以自行觀看~", "timestamp": "2023-12-04T11:17:17.997000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1181192502477324308", "filename": "-.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 613862, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1181192502104035458/1181192502477324308/-.jpg?ex=69fb233e&is=69f9d1be&hm=37170b41ab80e8102d3a6906d3730de0e0602d7c6bc490900a8feac2196dae9f&"}], "embeds": [{"type": "link", "title": "目錄索引.xlsx", "url": "https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1ahF_ULcWsj8Up9hT6qNzraKoE3Vlyhni/edit?usp=sharing&ouid=109622897795166533791&rtpof=true&sd=true", "description": "目錄索引\n\n「忘卻前夜」攻略全收錄\n前言：\n為方便各位更好並且及時可以看到關於「忘卻前夜」的攻略文，可以及時獲取到自己想要的信息，快速通關，特地在此處開設一個攻略手冊，即拿即用，隨時更新！！！該文主要收錄各平台優質攻略「均表明出處」，實時更新\n一.萌新入門篇\n遊戲系統介紹「必讀」\n了解遊戲基礎介面玩法，快速上手"}], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1181192502104035458", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "艾瑞卡攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526"]}
